text: Taranasha Wallace (born in September 20, 1976), known as Tara Wallace. She is American actress and television personality. She have been appear in Love & Hip Hop: New York and Love & Hip Hop: Atlanta. == Early life == She has a brother named Jackie Wallace. Wallace was born in McComb, Mississippi. == Personal life == Wallace started dating American rapper Peter Gunz in 2000. They have three sons together, born in 2008, 2012, and 2016. The couple split up in 2015. Category:Living people Category:1976 births Category:American actors Category:People from Mississippi
title: Tara Wallace
